w occurs here\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n[Playground link](https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=stable&mode=debug&edition=2018&gist=6793a9891d51f3ebd14557a98e4686f3)\r\n[Playground (version with if)](https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=stable&mode=debug&edition=2018&gist=9f5ac590f18c786764d3bfb0d288d6eb)\r\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/84361/reactions", "total_count": 6, "+1": 6, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/84361/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}